## ðŸ’¡2. CNN
>In accordance with the task requirements, systematic experiments were conducted on the hyperparameters of the CNN model, including kernel size, learning rate, and number of layers.

### ðŸ’¡2.1 Best CNN Model

* **Best test set accuracy:** **99.35%**
* **Optimal Parameters:**
  * `Kernel Size`: 3
  * `Learning Rate`: 0.001
  * `Number of Conv Layers`: 3

